OL,3,CPub sit-in marks 60 years since one
OL,4,Cman's protest made British history
OL,6,FCivil rights activists, community
OL,7,Fleaders and pioneers of the Bristol
OL,8,FBus Boycott have marked the 60th
OL,9,Fanniversary of one man's protest
OL,10,Fagainst a pub's colour bar with a mass
OL,11,Fsit-in.
OL,13,FOn 10 April 1964, civil rights leader
OL,14,FPaul Stephenson was arrested and put
OL,15,Fon trial for protesting against the
OL,16,FBay Horse Pub's policy of not serving
OL,17,Fblack people.
