OL,6,FThe magistrate threw out the charges
OL,7,Fand the case paved the way for the
OL,8,FRace Relations Act of 1965, the UK's
OL,9,Ffirst anti-racist law.
OL,11,FIn 1983, Dr Stephenson spoke to ITV
OL,12,FNews' Bruce Hockin about his historic
OL,13,Fstand.
OL,15,FHe said: "Large numbers of public
OL,16,Fhouses in those days weren't serving
OL,17,Fblack people. When I was told to get
OL,18,Fout because I was black, I thought
OL,19,Fthat's not on and so I stayed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
