OL,6,F"When the police came to arrest me I
OL,7,Fwas surprised to find about 15 police
OL,8,Fofficers, a Land Rover and a couple of
OL,9,Fdogs."
OL,11,FHe added: "Of course I went through an
OL,12,Fenormous ordeal, the emotional ordeal
OL,13,Fof being locked up.
OL,15,F"There was a young Irishman in that
OL,16,Fpublic house who I didn't know but
OL,17,Fcame to give evidence at the police
OL,18,Fstation to say that I hadn't done
OL,19,Fanything really bad and they told him
OL,20,Fto go away."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
