OL,6,FBruce Hockin asked him: "But what
OL,7,Fabout the court case and the result
OL,8,Fitself. How did you feel when it was
OL,9,Fall over?"
OL,11,FDr Stephenson replied: "Well it was
OL,12,Fvery terrible going through the actual
OL,13,Ftrial. As you know it was front page
OL,14,Fheadlines, it was a national issue and
OL,15,FI felt very much alone on that."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
