OL,6,FDr Stephenson went on to say: "More
OL,7,Fimportantly, it gave the Wilson
OL,8,FGovernment an even greater spur under
OL,9,Fthe then Home Secretary Roy Jenkins to
OL,10,Flegislate and they did a few months
OL,11,Flater.
OL,13,F"They were already considering it
OL,14,Fanyhow but I think it gave them an
OL,15,Fequal spur to legislate and the first
OL,16,FRace Relations Act was in 1965 and the
OL,17,Ffirst thing they did was make racial
OL,18,Fdiscrimination in public houses
OL,19,Fillegal."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
