OL,3,CPub sit-in marks 60 years since one
OL,4,Cman's protest made British history
OL,6,FIn recognition of the historic moment,
OL,7,Fthe Bay Horse Pub has formally
OL,8,Fapologised for the injustice that took
OL,9,Fplace there.
OL,11,FMark Howe, Business Development
OL,12,FManager said: "Everyone involved with
OL,13,Fthe pub wants to wholeheartedly
OL,14,Fapologise to Paul for the treatment he
OL,15,Freceived that day.
OL,17,F"This apology is not only to Paul
OL,18,FStephenson himself for the terrible
OL,19,Factions on that day in 1964 but also
OL,20,Fto the whole community whom this
OL,21,Faffected."
