OL,6,FThe pub also launched a new beer
OL,7,Fcalled The Sit-In as a tribute and
OL,8,Funveiled a brass plaque as Bristol's
OL,9,Ffirst public monument to Paul's
OL,10,Fachievements.
OL,12,FPaul, who is 87 (he was born on 6 May
OL,13,F1937), was unable to attend the
OL,14,Fcommemorations on Friday 25 October
OL,15,Fbut members of his family joined in
OL,16,Fthe events to mark his legacy.
OL,18,FWho is Paul Stephenson?
