OL,4,Cman's protest made British history
OL,6,FIn 2009 he was awarded an OBE, and an
OL,7,Fhonorary degree from the University of
OL,8,FThe West of England, and a honorary
OL,9,FDoctorate of Law from Bristol
OL,10,FUniversity in 2014.
OL,12,FIn 2017 Paul Stephenson received a
OL,13,FPride of Britain Lifetime Achievement
OL,14,FAward and shortly afterwards, Great
OL,15,FWestern Railway named a train after
OL,16,Fhim.
